# Login – Quick Traceability (no charts)

**Purpose:** One-screen map from requirements → test cases → result.  
**Env:** Windows 11 • Firefox  **Creds:** Admin / admin123

Legend: ✅ PASS 🟠 Defect logged 📝 Clarification/UX

| # | Requirement (what should happen)                                   | Test case(s)          | Result |
|---|--------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------|:------:|
| 1 | Valid login opens the dashboard                                    | TC-001, TC-012        | ✅ PASS |
| 2 | Username required when blank                                       | TC-002                | ✅ PASS |
| 3 | Password required when blank                                       | TC-003                | ✅ PASS |
| 4 | Wrong credentials show “Invalid credentials”                       | TC-004, TC-013        | ✅ PASS |
| 5 | Username case policy is handled (defined/insensitive)              | TC-005                | ✅ PASS |
| 6 | After **Logout**, pressing browser **Back** does **not** reopen app | TC-014                | 🟠 See DEF-014 |
| 7 | Password is masked; toggle works *if present*                      | TC-015                | 📝 See CLAR-002 |

